data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in a prime location! This stunning property boasts modern updates and is move-in ready. Step inside to discover charming shiplap walls adding character to the living spaces. Cozy up by the brick fireplace on chilly evenings or enjoy the scenic views from the balcony. The walk-out basement offers additional living space and convenience. With a spacious patio and fenced-in yard, outdoor entertaining is a breeze. Plus, keep your vehicles out of the westher in the attached garage. Don't miss this opportunity to own a stylish and functional home in a fantastic neighborhood. Schedule your showing today!
This is the listing agent's personal home. Closing costs, etc, are negotiable.
